window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From the number one international best-selling author of </b><b><i>Holy Island</i></b><b> and </b><b><i>Impostor</i></b><b>.</b></p> <p>From the shadows into the light....</p> <p>When a fishing boat is wrecked off the treacherous North Sea coast and the body of a young woman washes up on the beach beside the iconic ‘Marsden Rock’, DCI Ryan cannot ignore the call to duty.</p> <p>With one already dead and more human cargo missing from the wreckage, Ryan and his team race to find the remaining souls - before it’s too late and their investigation turns to murder. As they uncover the seedy underbelly of Tyneside, cold and calculated opportunism clashes with the rock-hard arm of the Law, but there’s one thing that proves stronger than stone....</p> <p>The human spirit.</p> <p>Murder and mystery are peppered with romance and humour in this fast-paced crime whodunnit set amidst the spectacular North Eastern landscape.</p>"; 
